    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM7.1">
<l>ālai nīḷkarum paṉṉavaṉ ṟālō vampu yattaṭaṅ kaṇṇiṉaṉṟālō</l>
<l>vēlai nīrniṟat taṉṉavaṉ ṟālō vēḻap pōtaka maṉṉavaṉ ṟālō</l>
<l>ēla vārkuḻa leṉmakaṉ ṟālō veṉṟeṉ ṟuṉṉaiyeṉ vāyiṭai niṟaiyat</l>
<l>tālo littiṭun tiruviṉai yillāt tāya riṟkaṭai yāyiṉa tāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O [You who are] like a long sugarcane from the press, tālō!</l>
<l>O [You] with long, lotus eyes, tālō!</l>
<l>O [You] of a hue similar to the ocean water, tālō!</l>
<l>O [You who are] like an elphant calf, tālō!</l>
<l>O my Son with long, unguent[-perfumed] curling hair, tālō!</l>
<l rend="indent">[I] have become the lowest among mothers,</l>
<l rend="indent">not having had the good karma to sing a lullaby to You,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying [this] again and again to the satisfaction of my mouth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
